00x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-White-Stripes-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-White-Stripes-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-White-Stripes-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/The-White-Stripes">白条纹乐队 (The White Stripes)</a>宣布为他们的第五张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7659-303871">Get Behind Me Saturday</a> 》发行 20 周年纪念特别版。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7659-303871">白色条纹：撒旦滚到我身后</a></strong></li></ul><p>新的重新发行版名为“Get Behind Me Saturday XX”，是<a href="/artists/Jack-white">Jack</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/meg-white">Meg White</a> 2005 年 LP 的姊妹版，其中包括歌曲创作演示、替代录音室录音以及原始专辑中曲目的现场版本。</p><p> 2xLP 黑胶唱片套装包含额外的 7 英寸唱片以及包含乐队 2005 年中南美巡演片段的蓝光光盘，更多内容将通过 The Vault – Third Man Record 的长期黑胶订阅服务提供。粉丝们可以<a href="https://n6thwjcab.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001-R5i05T-jGzeM5fuinYJHMuILh7iQIsMAHf-jUdRCBOWEEvP5OB7J5vNnbm4LvK7U8dLazJw69KOaL6rNB6Ojcm3mlc8X2fTaOOeIyNUtbb4LzHa-FGH_JzIrezFRIC3IwoTQIIm4gSCnMEu3cYWPdF3F1XZc06Ni6Aiudr0-zbEs0FOCdgdbdg1cDbfEXkm&amp;c=L6qY9h9tKXnYscnuyQ7BQLD3iUGTFay32dOEZNQECVX58r6P6aZ_9g==&amp;ch=3MjaJa-G-DCSjPboBOyq82Qx23T54NawiYpNz-ZpDsweMHfHLaD5gA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>订阅该套餐。 “Get Behind Me Saturday XX”套餐的截止日期为 2025 年 1 月 31 日上午 12 点（中部时间）。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEnF7xWRXXP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; 